BYU Young Ambassadors to perform live at BYU-Idaho
The BYU Young Ambassadors will open the Center Stage Winter 2020 season with their fun, high-energy musical theater performance on January 16 at 7:30 p.m. in the Hart Auditorium.
BYU-Idaho’s Center Stage to showcase six live performances in Winter 2020
The Center Stage Performing Arts Series at Brigham Young University-Idaho has announced its Winter 2020 Semester lineup of performances.
2018 BYU-Idaho Christmas concert to be broadcast on Idaho Public Television
Brigham Young University-Idaho’s 2018 performance of “A BYU-Idaho Christmas” will be broadcast across the state on Idaho Public Television (IdahoPTV).
